   <conbody>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Log in to the web interface to change the
IP address of the NMC.</p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">To configure the TCP/IP IPv4 settings:<ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Navigate to <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Configuration &gt; Network&gt;
TCP/IP &gt; IPv4 Settings</uicontrol>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Here you can:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Enable IPv4</p>
                           </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Set a manual IP address, subnet mask and default gateway.</p>
                           </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Enable BOOTP or DHCP</p>
                           </li>
                        </ul>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">To enter a new manual IP address:<ol class="- topic/ol ">
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Make sure IPv4 is enabled.</p>
                           </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Make sure <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Manual</uicontrol> mode
is selected.</p>
                           </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Enter the new IP address in the field <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">System IP</uicontrol>.</p>
                           </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Click <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Apply</uicontrol>.</p>
                           </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">The IP address is now changed.</p>
                              <note conref="../Library/Reference_Library_CPT_0000338844.dita#Reference_Library-69E2C789/restart_to_apply_change"
                                    class="- topic/note ">A reboot of the NMC might be necessary to activate changes.</note>
                           </li>
                        </ol>
                     </p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">To configure the TCP/IP IPv6 settings:<ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Navigate to <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Configuration &gt; Network&gt;
TCP/IP &gt; IPv6 Settings</uicontrol>.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Here you can:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Enable IPv6</p>
                           </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Enable IPv6 auto configuration</p>
                           </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Set a manual IP address and default gateway.</p>
                           </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Enable different DHCPv6 modes</p>
                           </li>
                        </ul>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">To enter a new manual IP address:<ol class="- topic/ol ">
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Make sure IPv6 is enabled.</p>
                           </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Make sure <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Manual Configuration</uicontrol> is enabled and <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Auto Configuration</uicontrol> is disabled.</p>
                           </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Enter the new IP address in the field <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">System IP</uicontrol>.</p>
                           </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Click <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Apply</uicontrol>.</p>
                           </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li ">
                              <p class="- topic/p ">The IP address is now changed.</p>
                              <note conref="../Library/Reference_Library_CPT_0000338844.dita#Reference_Library-69E2C789/restart_to_apply_change"
                                    class="- topic/note ">A reboot of the NMC might be necessary to activate changes.</note>
                           </li>
                        </ol>
                     </p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </p>
